::Ursa Major::

"Ursa Major Maximaize!"
She transforms into bot mode and fires on Bumblebee.  She jumps and rolls to 
Striker.

"You going to be OK?"

She turned and fired a few shots on the Turantulus.  She turned and looked 
at Ramulus.

"Ramulus, You get the mouse.  I'll do my best to cover you."

She fired on Turantulus.  She raised her other gun and fired on Bumblebee.  
She had both weapons drawn and firing with both of them.
